data.description: You won’t want to miss this lovely 6 years young, split level home in sought after Falcon Lakes, Basehor neighborhood. Upon entering you’ll be greeted with the spacious and open concept this home has to offer. From vaulted ceilings to its large yard, this home is perfect for all. While the huge master suite sits just a few steps above the second floor, you’ll notice all 3 bedrooms are generous in size.  On top of the 1,800 sqft of this home, the unfinished basement and sub-basement are perfect for storage, but also offer lots of light, so the opportunities are endless.
